    <summary>Defines CICP (Coding-independent Code Points) color primaries per ITU-T H.273.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKColorspacePrimariesCicp` enumerates standardized color primaries as defined by ITU-T H.273. These values are used with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp*> to create color spaces for wide-gamut and HDR content.

## Examples

```csharp
var cs = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(
    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec2020,
    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Pq);
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
